{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7e6f55fd-1ebf-53f4-87dc-c1ee18816b8e","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/3ac88/image-4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/8ac56/image-4.webp 240w,\n/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/d3be9/image-4.webp 480w,\n/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/e46b2/image-4.webp 960w,\n/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/4ef06/image-4.webp 1260w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/09b79/image-4.jpg 240w,\n/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/7cc5e/image-4.jpg 480w,\n/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/6a068/image-4.jpg 960w,\n/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/3ac88/image-4.jpg 1260w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/eb3a3a2300ef1b86ae82739a5cb4cccf/6a068/image-4.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper. Aenean ultricies mi vitae est. Mauris placerat eleifend leo. Quisque sit amet est et sapien ullamcorper pharetra. Vestibulum erat wisi, condimentum sed, commodo vitae, ornare sit amet, wisi.\"\n            title=\"Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper. Aenean ultricies mi vitae est. Mauris placerat eleifend leo. Quisque sit amet est et sapien ullamcorper pharetra. Vestibulum erat wisi, condimentum sed, commodo vitae, ornare sit amet, wisi.\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hi\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hi\" aria-label=\"hi permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hi!</h3>\n<p>I now live in Maastricht, The Netherland and work on <a href=\"https://www.maastrichtuniversity.nl/p70069673\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Maastricht University</a> - at the <a href=\"https://www.maastrichtuniversity.nl/research/institute-data-science\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Institute of Data Science</a> as data scientist. </p>\n<p>Technologies I’m learning in 2021 are: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Semantic_Web\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Semantic Web</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linked_data\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Linked Open Data</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge_graph\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Knowledge Graphs</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/React_(web_framework)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">React</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"research-interests\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#research-interests\" aria-label=\"research interests permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Research Interests</h3>\n<p>My research interests lie in two distant but related fields: the development of geographic thought and representation in Antiquity and the Middle Ages, and the emerging role of the Web as a transformational medium for communicating and connecting complex information.I have an ongoing interest in digital humanities - both in deep history and ancient world - and computational archaeology.</p>\n<p><a href=\"src/static/media/CV.pdf\">download</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"reading\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reading\" aria-label=\"reading permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reading</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Next:</li>\n<li>Current:<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epistulae_Morales_ad_Lucilium\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Letters from a Stoic</a></li>\n<li>Past: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enchiridion_of_Epictetus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Enchiridion</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"quote\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#quote\" aria-label=\"quote permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quote</h3>\n<figure class=\"float-right\" style=\"width: 240px\">\n\t<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 440px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/dd2b39406f687cd4c7a105f48c2ac16d/fe55e/epicetus.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 176.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/dd2b39406f687cd4c7a105f48c2ac16d/8ac56/epicetus.webp 240w,\n/static/dd2b39406f687cd4c7a105f48c2ac16d/23a50/epicetus.webp 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/dd2b39406f687cd4c7a105f48c2ac16d/09b79/epicetus.jpg 240w,\n/static/dd2b39406f687cd4c7a105f48c2ac16d/fe55e/epicetus.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/dd2b39406f687cd4c7a105f48c2ac16d/fe55e/epicetus.jpg\" alt=\"Epicetus\" title=\"Epicetus\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n\t<figcaption>Epicetus</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n\t<blockquote>\n\t\t<p>Never proclaim yourself as philosopher , [....], do not discourse how people ought to eat; but eat as you ought. Thus, do you not make an exhibition before the ignorarnt of your principles; but of the actions to which their digestion gives rise.</p>\n\t\t<footer>\n\t\t\t<cite>—XLVI Chapter, Enchiridion, AD c. 125</cite>\n\t\t</footer>\n\t</blockquote></figure>","frontmatter":{"title":"About me","date":null,"description":null,"socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/3432987dc3af66bb536c88d0b4911dc4/image-2.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/about/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}